version_description: Join the Cookie Cats across 30 new levels as they take flight to save the Kittens! New adventures around every corner! Play the daily events while you cruise along the beautifully handcrafted map and levels, and help the Cookie Cats save the day!

The cats are hittin’ the road and heading on down to Route 66, for a fast driving, leather jacket wearing, swing dancing adventure! Get ready for a rockin’ good time!

• 50 new levels! Rock around the clock till there’s no levels left!

The cats are hittin’ the road and heading on down to Route 66, for a fast driving, leather jacket wearing, swing dancing adventure! Get ready for a rockin’ good time!

• 50 new levels! Rock around the clock till there’s no levels left!

Join the cats for a colorful tradition and sharing of tails. Come, take a skull biscuit and be part of the celebration!

• 30 new levels! Don't become a scaredy-cat, join the paw-rade!

Follow the gang into the wild. Adventorous, relaxing or mesmerizing, the trip beyond the forest frontier is bound to bringa a cozy autumn feel to you.

• Discover the 40 new levels hidden under the leaves.

• Discover the 40 new levels hidden under the leaves.

Join us at the ski resort for many cozy winter nights. If you're lucky, you might even find Santa or his sleigh.
Make the snowy trek to the cabin and let's dash, slalom and have mountains of fun!
• A 40-level slope is waiting just for you!

Lights, Camera, ACTION! The cats are working hard for their big screen debut! So come along with us and see our rising stars, and movie magic in the making!
30 stops on the set tour

Lights, Camera, ACTION! The cats are working hard for their big screen debut! So come along with us and see our rising stars, and movie magic in the making!
30 stops on the set tour

Paws and relax for a moment before you turn over a mew leaf! The promise of spring is right around the corner. Join the gang in the Zen Garden, for a cup of hot tea.
30 levels are waiting on the stone path

Love is in the air, cats are in the clouds! Find or grab your sweetheart and cuddle up for a purrfect day to last fur-ever.
Enjoy 30 sweet moments on us.

Love is in the air, cats are in the clouds! Find or grab your sweetheart and cuddle up for a purrfect day to last fur-ever.
Enjoy 30 sweet moments on us.

Cookies are missing! We have a cat burglar on the loose! The gang is split: Some chose the path of justice; some dipped their paw too deep into the cookie jar. Which side are you on? Better not get caught red-pawed!
Investigate 30 new levels and find out who is behind the theft!

The sun is shining, there's a smell of fresh cookies in the air: spring is here!
Invitations have been sent for all the cats to join our purr-fect little garden party.
Join us in purr-suit of Easter eggs and bunny hop through 30 new levels!

The sun is shining, there's a smell of fresh cookies in the air: spring is here!
Invitations have been sent for all the cats to join our purr-fect little garden party.
Join us in purr-suit of Easter eggs and bunny hop through 30 new levels!

Tulips and cafe's: time to strecth out, scratch off the laziness and break-away with the cats ! Smokey and Belle went traveling through the canals. Join them! or purr-haps you'd like to join Ziggy on his brand new boat!
Wonder what Berry is up to ? You have 30 levels to find out!

Wonder what Berry is up to ? You have 30 levels to find out!

Tag, you're it! Come play with the kittens on their new kittengarden playground!
Chase them through these 30 new levels! Last one is a slow paw!

The beach is one big kitty sandbox: whether you like to snorkel, enjoy an ice cream, get a fine tan or build an intricate sand sculpture, the cats have just the thing for you.
30 sunny levels ready for a splash.

The lazy-hazy-crazy summer continues!  It's all about fun, games and contests. Will you beat the cats at a pie eating contest ? Better get the highest score in all the 40 levels they prepared for you!

Sneak around and help the cats thwart the villain's plans before the count-down runs out!
Discover 50 new devious plans that the ultimate evil meowstermind has set up and untangle them all!

The cats would like to welcome you into the halls of Cathalla! Come and prove your worth! Claim your place at Meowdin's table through these 30 brand new levels.

Once upon a time, there were 5 furry, mischievous meow-nificent cats.
Ziggy says that they lived happily ever after once the villains turned them into toads.
Find out if that's true in the 30 levels they've purr-pared for you!
Meow-ho, meow-ho, and off to the mines we go! Help the kitties dig through these 30 brand new levels, and you might find meowntains of gold stars for yourself!
Ahoy! The boats are fit, the rods are ready, 30 fishing spots to visit before the winter hits. Cats paws ahead!

There are some purranormal happenings taking place in cookie cats land! Will you help the cats uncover the mysteries this Meowloween? There are 30 spooky new levels to be explored, so don't be a scardy cat!

Grab your coat and enjoy the snowy WINTER WONDERLAND throughout 50 new levels!
